Create tailwind.config.cjs (or .js) with content: ['./index.html','./src/**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}'] and darkMode: 'class'.

Create src/main.jsx that mounts <App /> inside <BrowserRouter> and wraps providers (Theme + I18n placeholders).

Create src/App.jsx with Routes: / (Home), /login (Login), /dashboard (Dashboard).

Create src/pages/Home.jsx which uses axios to GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/hello/ on mount and displays the message.

Add index.css with Tailwind base/components/utilities and a CSS variable :root { --brand: #c56926 }.

Add scripts in package.json for dev, build, preview.

Generate full file contents for all created files and explain how to run npm run dev.

